Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner of the house messes the room up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And something disappears so there was a great fuss over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I file this as a case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really going to be struck by my boss' thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, god how frightening, ha, ha, ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Butoit is a fact-that I scared the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you pack the dolls as a token of my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that you can take it home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, on second thought,\NI'm not going to take it!
