Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because it warded off evil in my place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'll try asking daddy again if he'll get it repaired for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry: after you went out of your way to help me line the dolls up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Girls' Festival doll that I really wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I really, really want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I really, really want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care what but,
