Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to take a picture of this sunset, right? Akemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, you sit right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.73,0:22:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, Ai and Genta, sit one step below!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please sét'the camera!
